article.headline: Santa Clara 84, Pacifica 59
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- Kevin Foster and Raymond Cowels III scored 14 points each to lead Santa Clara to an 84-59 victory against Pacifica College on Tuesday night. John McArthur had 12 points and seven rebounds and Evan Roquemore 10 points for the Broncos (6-3). Alex Brandon scored 13 points and Craig Levinson and Terry Beazley 12 apiece for the Gladiators (2-10). Leading 37-31 at the break, Santa Clara opened the second half with a 19-6 to take permanent control. McArthur had eight points during the surge.
